help:
             Press : to open the console, then write the command.

   The list of commands:
        close                          - destroys opened space
        help                           - shows help
        history                        - shows the history of commands
        map                            - (un)assigns command to key
        n[ew]                          - creates new space
        o[pen]                         - opens figure from file
        (q[uit]|exit)                  - closes the application
        reset boundary                 - removes the figure except vertices
        reset colors                   - sets the default colors
        reset rot[ation]               - rotates figure to its default rotation
        rmap                           - (un)assigns rotation to key
        rot[ate]                       - rotates figure
        set                            - shows/edits settings
        so[urce]                       - executes python script
        vert[ex] add                   - adds new vertex
        vert[ex] desel[ect]            - deselects the vertex
        vert[ex] move                  - moves the selected vertex
        vert[ex] ( prev[ious] | next ) - cycles over the vertices
        vert[ex] r[e]m[ove]            - removes the selected vertex
        vert[ex] sel[ect]              - selects specified vertex
        w[rite]                        - writes figure to a file

                      For more help type :help <command>.
For information about scripting and default configuration type :help python.
     For information about author and license conditions type :help about.
